generatedPrompts.frontCover:
{
  "frontCover": "Front cover of a greeting card in a 9:16 aspect ratio, rendered in a bold Pop Art style reminiscent of Andy Warhol and Roy Lichtenstein. The background is a vibrant, sunny yellow, adorned with a repeating pattern of simple, stylized green cacti. The primary subject is a smiling, stylized illustration of a man with dark hair and a beard, wearing a dark teal t-shirt with a white stylized 'A' logo. His head is turned to the right, with a cheerful expression. Above and to his right, a yellow thought bubble with a halftone dot pattern contains an illustration of a prickly pear cactus with a single red flower. To the left of the man's head, a white speech bubble contains an illustration of a black briefcase. To the right of the cactus thought bubble, a white speech bubble contains a stylized blue globe icon, and below that, another white speech bubble contains a blue plus sign. The greeting text \"Kudos to you!\" is prominently displayed in a large, dark blue, flowing, handwritten cursive script across the top of the card, with the exclamation mark emphasizing the celebratory tone. The overall mood is upbeat and encouraging, with a clear, graphic aesthetic and bold color blocking. The image utilizes clean lines and flat colors with halftone dot textures to achieve the Pop Art look. The overall impression is one of aspiration and positive anticipation.",
  "backCover": "Back cover of a greeting card in a 9:16 aspect ratio, continuing the Pop Art style with a vibrant yellow background featuring a repeating pattern of stylized green cacti. The design is minimal and serene, focusing on a single, stylized, red and orange prickly pear cactus flower in the center-left portion of the card. The flower is depicted with bold outlines and flat colors, echoing the style of the front cover, but without any text or speech/thought bubbles. The bottom-right corner, approximately a 1-inch square, is left completely clear and undecorated. The overall mood is a gentle, artistic conclusion, subtly referencing the motif from the front cover.",
  "leftInterior": "Left interior of a greeting card in a 9:16 aspect ratio, continuing the Pop Art style. The background is a vibrant, sunny yellow, with a repeating pattern of stylized green cacti. The left side features a large, stylized speech bubble with a yellow interior and a white outline, emanating from the bottom edge and curving upwards towards the center. Inside this speech bubble, a cluster of stylized green cacti with small black dots is depicted, similar to the motif on the front cover. A single red prickly pear cactus flower blooms from one of the cacti. Small, white circular 'bubbles' or highlights are scattered around the cactus illustration within the speech bubble, adding a touch of dynamism. The overall composition is clean and graphic, maintaining the cheerful and encouraging tone of the card.",
  "rightInterior": "Right interior of a greeting card in a 9:16 aspect ratio, rendered in the same bold Pop Art style. The background is a vibrant yellow with a repeating pattern of stylized green cacti. Dominating the center of the card is an artistic, flowing composition designed to showcase the message. The message \"you will find a job and build your cactee startup turning cactus into a sustainable vegan leather, and Impact the world, keep the spirit up change maker!\" is written in a beautiful, clearly readable, flowing handwritten cursive script in dark blue, with a slight handwritten pen-like appearance. The script is integrated into an abstract, flowing design that uses elements inspired by the front cover, such as stylized cacti shapes and bold color accents in yellow, green, and red. The overall impression is a visually engaging and personalized message space, avoiding any literal depictions of people or objects, and focusing on the artistic framing of the encouraging text."
